【answer】step1:Because $V_{e}=50.00 \mathrm{~mL}$, the fraction of $\mathrm{I}^{-}$reacted is $49.00 / 50.00$, and the fraction remaining is $1.00 / 50.00$. The total volume is $25.00+49.00=74.00 \mathrm{~mL}$.

$\begin{aligned}
{\left[\mathrm{I}^{-}\right] } & =\underbrace{\left(\frac{1.00}{50.00}\right)}_{\begin{array}{c}
