{\left[\mathrm{Ag}^{+}\right] } & =K_{\mathrm{sp}} /\left[\mathrm{I}^{-}\right]=\left(8.3 \times 10^{-17}\right) /\left(6.76 \times 10^{-4}\right)=1.2_3 \times 10^{-13} \mathrm{M} \\
